<b_left_sidehead_nonum>Survival</b_left_sidehead_nonum>
  <numbered_2_para>The termination or determination of this Contract howsoever arising shall not operate to affect such of the provisions under this Contract which in accordance with their terms are expressed to operate or have effect after the termination or determination of this Contract. For the avoidance of doubt, provisions that shall survive the termination and/or determination of this Contract include without limitation, those relating to Confidential Information, Rights, Work, and the effect of termination or determination.</numbered_2_para>

<b_left_sidehead_nonum>No contra proferentum</b_left_sidehead_nonum>
  <numbered_2_para>Contractor hereby represents that, in executing this Contract she has had the opportunity (whether or not actually undertaken) to seek the advice of independent legal counsel, and she has read and understood all of the terms and provisions of this Contract. In the interpretation of this Contract or any part thereof, no rule of construction shall apply to the disadvantage of any Party on the basis that that Party (i) prepared this Contract or any part of it; or (ii) seeks to rely on this Contract or any part of it.</numbered_2_para>

<b_left_sidehead_nonum>No waiver</b_left_sidehead_nonum>
  <numbered_2_para>No failure on the part of any Party to exercise, and no delay on the part of any Party in exercising any right under this Contract, will operate as a release or waiver thereof, nor will any single or partial exercise of any right under this Contract preclude any other or further exercise of it.</numbered_2_para>

<b_left_sidehead_nonum>Counterparts</b_left_sidehead_nonum>
  <numbered_2_para>This Contract may be executed in one or more counterparts, and such counterparts may be exchanged by electronic transmission (including by email), each of which will be deemed an original but all of which together constitute one and the same agreement. In the case of execution by way of counterparts, this Contract shall not be deemed as concluded until the last of such counterparts is duly signed and delivered to the other Party.</numbered_2_para>

<b_left_sidehead_nonum>Variation</b_left_sidehead_nonum>
